videos.headline: Burrow: 'Look at us now'
videos.description: Joe Burrow reflects on LSU's victory in the SEC title game and says this championship run was always his expectation.

videos.headline: Orgeron: Burrow is the greatest LSU recruit
videos.description: Ed Orgeron reacts to LSU's SEC title victory and explains why Joe Burrow may be the greatest recruit LSU ever had.
